  "prompt": "Which are the companies that hire freshers in Analytics (R programming)?",
  "response": "Many companies across different industries hire freshers for analytics roles that require skills in R programming. Here are some notable ones:\n\n1. **Accenture** - A global consulting and professional services firm that often hires freshers for various analytics roles.\n2. **Deloitte** - Known for its consulting and advisory services, Deloitte recruits freshers for analytics positions.\n3. **KPMG** - Another major consulting firm that hires freshers for roles in data analytics.\n4. **PwC (PricewaterhouseCoopers)** - Offers opportunities in analytics and data science for freshers.\n5. **IBM** - A leading technology and consulting company that recruits freshers for analytics roles.\n6. **Capgemini** - Provides consulting, technology, and outsourcing services, including analytics positions for freshers.\n7. **Tata Consultancy Services (TCS)** - One of the largest IT services firms, hiring freshers for analytics roles.\n8. **Infosys** - An IT services company that recruits freshers for data analytics positions.\n9. **Wipro** - Offers various roles in analytics and data science for freshers.\n10. **Mu Sigma** - A decision sciences and big data analytics firm that often hires freshers.\n11. **Fractal Analytics** - Focuses on AI and analytics solutions and recruits freshers.\n12. **ZS Associates** - A management consulting firm specializing in analytics and sales force effectiveness, hiring freshers.\n13. **Genpact** - A global professional services firm that recruits freshers for analytics roles.\n14. **EXL Service** - Focuses on operations management and analytics, hiring freshers.\n15. **Cognizant** - An IT services company that offers analytics roles for freshers.\n16. **Ernst & Young (EY)** - A global professional services firm that hires freshers for analytics positions.\n17. **Amazon** - Known for its e-commerce and technology services, Amazon hires freshers for data analytics roles.\n18. **Google** - Offers various roles in data analytics for freshers.\n19. **Facebook (Meta)** - Provides opportunities in data analytics for freshers.\n20. **LinkedIn** - Hires freshers for analytics roles.\n21. **Flipkart** - An e-commerce company that recruits freshers for analytics positions.\n22. **Adobe** - Offers roles in data analytics for freshers.\n23. **Microsoft** - Hires freshers for various analytics roles.\n24. **Uber** - Provides opportunities in data analytics for freshers.\n\nThese companies offer various entry-level positions, internships, and graduate programs that can help freshers start their careers in analytics with a focus on R programming. It\u2019s advisable to check their career pages and job portals for the latest openings tailored to fresh graduates.",
